  "special": {
    "description": "Consumes 1 ammo per shot but fires 3 projectiles. The spread forms a smiling face and shifts from tight, to wide, then back again as it travels. While held, it grants 4% life steal from all damage you deal.",
    "title": "We're all mad here. I'm mad. You're mad."
  },
  "notes": "Gaige can exploit it with Close Enough, as the high fire rate and multiple projectiles per shot create a steady stream of ricochets. Anarchy cuts its practical range even further. Krieg also pairs well with it at close range, especially with Hellborn for elemental pressure and healing, while Bloodlust benefits from the weapon's ammo efficiency and large magazine.",
